R versus python

This is a big topic, but here are a few links to get started. Lately the two seem to be converging in terms of usage (i.e.there is a trend towards using both together, read the latest news from Rstudiosee the first link)

  • Posit Why RStudio Is Changing Its Name
  • R Vs Python: Whats the Difference?
  • R vs.Python: Which is a better programming language for data science?
  • Why Ill stick with R
